Definition: grossly offensive to decency or morality
Example: causing horror; subjected to outrageous cruelty; a hideous pattern of injustice; horrific conditions in the mining industry
Synonyms: horrid, noun, attribute, horridness, horrific, outrageous, event, outrage, outrageousness, grossly, offensive, to, decency, or, morality, causing, horror, subjected, cruelty, a, pattern, of, injustice, conditions, in, the, mining, industry
Category: adj.all
